&lt;/div&gt;</description></item><item><title>Image gallery</title><link>https://demo.stack.jimmycai.com/p/image-gallery/</link><pubDate>Sat, 26 Aug 2023 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://demo.stack.jimmycai.com/p/image-gallery/</guid><description>&lt;img src="https://demo.stack.jimmycai.com/p/image-gallery/2.jpg" alt="Featured image of post Image gallery" /&gt;&lt;p&gt;Hugo theme Stack supports the creation of interactive image galleries using Markdown. It&amp;rsquo;s powered by &lt;a class="link" href="https://photoswipe.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
&gt;PhotoSwipe&lt;/a&gt; and its syntax was inspired by &lt;a class="link" href="https://typlog.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
&gt;Typlog&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;To use this feature, the image must be in the same directory as the Markdown file, as it uses Hugo&amp;rsquo;s page bundle feature to read the dimensions of the image. &lt;strong&gt;External images are not supported.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id="syntax"&gt;Syntax
